.TH "pci_rescan_bus" 9 "pci_rescan_bus" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pci_rescan_bus \- Scan a PCI bus for devices
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "unsigned int" pci_rescan_bus
.BI "(struct pci_bus *bus "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bus" 12
PCI bus to scan
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Scan a PCI bus and child buses for new devices, add them,
and enable them.

Returns the max number of subordinate bus discovered.
